    <title>pip is not defined</title>
    <link href="http://eigie.org/posts/EPlZrROlr9FPxh6pKfwHLw/"/>
    <id>http://eigie.org/posts/EPlZrROlr9FPxh6pKfwHLw/</id>
    <published>2015-12-06T04:22:07.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-08-06T11:42:12.623Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://7xoim3.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/2015-12-06sunlight-in-dongchuan-kunming-by-fabrizio-massetti.jpg" alt="--"><a href="https://500px.com/photo/131255549/sunlight-in-dongchuan-kunming-by-fabrizio-massetti" target="_blank" rel="external">图片原作者</a></p>
<p>更新了Anaconda后之前的一些包没有了。比如：chardet与pyquery。而<a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/4750806/how-to-install-pip-on-windows" target="_blank" rel="external">python 3.4之后是自带pip的</a>，所以可以直接用pip安装。由于之前没有真正用pip安装过，所以安装过程是一波又三折。</p>
<p>#pip 无法运行</p>
<p>按照<a href="https://pip.pypa.io/en/latest/user_guide/#installing-packages" target="_blank" rel="external">官方文档</a>，看起来蛮容易的：</p>
<pre><code>$ pip install SomePackage            # latest version
$ pip install SomePackage==1.0.4     # specific version
$ pip install &apos;SomePackage&gt;=1.0.4&apos;   # minimum version
</code></pre><p>但是却出现了：<br><img src="http://7xoim3.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/2015-12-06pip-not-defined.PNG" alt="NameError: name &#39;pip&#39; is not defined"><br>和<br><img src="http://7xoim3.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/2015-12-06pip-install-SyntaxError.PNG" alt="pip install chardet \n SyntaxError: invalid syntax"></p>
<p>这个是由于在python的交互console去执行pip导致的。。。<br>正确的执行方法是在windows的cmd下：</p>
<pre><code>python -m pip install pyquery
</code></pre><p>或者是将”Anaconda3\Scripts”也加入环境变量，然后就可以在cmd下直接执行:</p>
<pre><code>pip install pyquery
</code></pre><p>#pip 无法连接到<a href="https://pypi.python.org/" target="_blank" rel="external">PiPy</a>导致安装失败</p>
<p>这个原因嘛多半是因为GFW。要解决可以找找看有没有其它地方有这个包，比如<a href="https://github.com/gawel/pyquery" target="_blank" rel="external">pyquery在github上有</a>。<br>因此可以用<a href="https://pip.pypa.io/en/latest/reference/pip_install/#editable-installs" target="_blank" rel="external">下面的办法安装</a>：</p>
<pre><code>pip install -e git+https://github.com/gawel/pyquery.git#egg=pyquery
</code></pre><p>当然也可以打包下到local后再用pip安装:</p>
<pre><code>pip install -e path/to/project       # project in another directory
</code></pre>]]></content>
    
